Review Text: Ordered Mutton kheema pulao and it tasted very good. For non spicy people it might feel uncomfortable but if you are a spicy lover, then you will enjoy

Located in the newly opened drive-in in Gachibowli. Dropped by for a late night meal..
Must say, the pulao was very delicious. Tried egg pulao - perfect spice levels and the right quantity for the money you pay..
Totally impressed with the taste here...
Suggestion - will taste even better when served hot!
Had a chicken pulav and Mirchi bhaji. The chicken pulav is excellent in taste with a perfect blend of spices and the Mirchi bhaji is decent. A must try outlet here.
